sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant F as Next.js Frontend
    participant S as Spring Boot Backend
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant P as OAuth Provider (Google/GitHub)

    alt OAuth login
        U->>F: Click "Sign in with Google/GitHub"
        F->>P: Redirect to provider consent screen
        P->>F: Redirect back with auth code
        F->>S: Send auth code
        S->>P: Exchange code for identity
        P->>S: Confirm identity (email, name, avatar)
        S->>DB: Find or create User record
    else Email/Username + Password
        U->>F: Submit credentials
        F->>S: POST /auth/login
        S->>DB: Look up user, verify password hash (BCrypt)
    end

    S->>DB: Create Session (store hashed refresh token)
    S->>F: Return JWT access token + httpOnly refresh cookie
    F->>U: Logged in, redirect to dashboard

    Note over F,S: On subsequent requests
    F->>S: Request with Authorization: Bearer <access token>
    S->>S: Validate JWT signature + expiry
    alt Access token expired
        F->>S: POST /auth/refresh (refresh cookie sent automatically)
        S->>DB: Validate refresh token against Sessions table
        S->>F: New access token
    end
